</ref>，且在首周的销量累计达到了219,000份。<ref name="billboard1">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1555888/macklemore-ryan-lewis-top-hot-100-imagine-dragons-ariana-grande-hit-top-10 |title=Macklemore & Ryan Lewis Top Hot 100; Imagine Dragons, Ariana Grande Hit Top 10 |publisher=[[告示板|告示板]] |language=en |date=2008-02-16 |accessdate=2013-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170214212901/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1555888/macklemore-ryan-lewis-top-hot-100-imagine-dragons-ariana-grande-hit-top-10 |archive-date=2017-02-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该专辑中还收录了《宝贝，我...》("Baby I")和与[[底特律|底特律]]说唱艺人[[大肖恩|大肖恩]]合作的单曲《就在那里》("Right There")。<ref>{{cite web |author=July 15, 2013 2:00pm EDT by Avery Thompson |url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2013/07/15/ariana-grande-baby-i-new-single/ |title=Ariana Grande: ‘Baby I’ — Singer Reveals Name Of New Single |publisher=Hollywood Life |language=en |date=2013-07-15 |accessdate=2013-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629033616/https://hollywoodlife.com/2013/07/15/ariana-grande-baby-i-new-single/ |archive-date=2019-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770708/ariana-grande-big-sean-masquerade-in-right-there-video-watch|title=Ariana Grande, Big Sean Masquerade in 'Right There' Video: Watch|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|date=2013-10-30|publisher=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示板杂志]]|language=en|accessdate=2014-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712031345/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5770708/ariana-grande-big-sean-masquerade-in-right-there-video-watch|archive-date=2019-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>

