专辑《挚爱》（''Yours Truly''）共用3年时间制作完成。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nostro|first1=Lauren|title=Who Is Ariana Grande?|url=http://www.complex.com/music/2013/08/who-is-ariana-grande/yours-truly|website=Complex|language=en|date=2013-08-27|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180912171651/https://www.complex.com/music/2013/08/who-is-ariana-grande/yours-truly|archive-date=2018-09-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>在制作过程中，制作理念和演唱方式都发生了不小的改动。格兰德早在2010年8月便开始了专辑的制作，但那时她还在忙着拍摄《[[胜利之歌|胜利之歌]]》。直到2011年8月10日，她与[[聯眾唱片|聯眾唱片]]公司正式签约后，制作进度才明显加快。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hyman|first1=Dan|title=Life Is Grande: Ariana Grande On Her Debut Album and the Thrill of Hearing Herself on the Radio|url=http://www.elle.com/news/culture/ariana-grande-interview|website=Elle|publisher=Hearst Communications, Inc.|language=en|date=2013-08-22|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108153902/http://www.elle.com/news/culture/ariana-grande-interview|archive-date=2014-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Grande|first=Ariana|title=Ariana Grande tweets picture of contract|url=https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/101471210382180353|publisher=Twitter|language=en|accessdate=2011-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005034639/https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/101471210382180353|archive-date=2013-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Universal Republic Records Announces the Signing of Ariana Grande|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/11/idUS232814+11-Aug-2011+BW20110811$$495411498|publisher=Reuters|language=en|date=2011-08-11|accessdate=2011-08-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403122946/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/11/idUS232814+11-Aug-2011+BW20110811$$495411498|archivedate=2015-04-03}}</ref>同年9月，她已经准备了20首歌曲，并决定将专辑中的收录曲目压缩至13首。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Talks Music at the Creative Arts Emmy Awards 2011|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6meF2HNv2sA#at=208|publisher=YouTube|language=en|date=|accessdate=2011-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022071047/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6meF2HNv2sA#at=208|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>第一首歌曲《捧起你的心》("Put Your Hearts Up")于2011年12月12日公布，属于{{link-en|泡泡糖流行乐|bubblegum pop}}风格。<ref>{{cite news|title=Ariana Grande Debuts New Single, 'Put Your Hearts Up'|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/12/12/ariana-grande-debuts-new-_n_1143349.html|publisher=Huffington Post|first=Carolyn|last=Gregoire|language=en|date=2011-12-12|accessdate=2011-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120115111540/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/12/12/ariana-grande-debuts-new-_n_1143349.html|archive-date=2012-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>这首歌是面向青少年听众的，因为亞莉安娜当时因出演《胜利之歌》在青少年中拥有了一定的人气，所以他们也是定位的核心听众。在2012年6月接受的一次采访中，亞莉安娜说专辑里的一切元素都是受“五六十年代[[嘟·喔普|doo-wop]]的影响而创作的”，而且会有2首歌在专辑正式发售前提前发售。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Talks New Album Being "Right Out Of Her Diary"|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CYTS2aI_m64|publisher=YouTube|language=en|date=|accessdate=2012-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022071103/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CYTS2aI_m64|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年，亞莉安娜向唱片公司表达了自己对专辑制作方向定位的不满。在13年的几次采访中，她都提到了自己完全不喜欢首单《捧起你的心》，也表示对那种风格的音乐没有兴趣。<ref>{{cite web|last=Grande|first=Ariana|title=Ariana Grande on KIIS-FM|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CuTS9Wf-PU8|publisher=Youtube|language=en|date=|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131027095015/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CuTS9Wf-PU8|archive-date=2013-10-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>她表示虽然自己目前在《萨姆和卡特》中饰演的是一名小孩，但希望今后所唱歌曲的内容能更多地体现出她性格成熟的一面。<ref>{{cite web|last=Grande|first=Ariana|title=Ariana Grande talks The Way|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|publisher=Billboard|language=en|date=|access-date=2014-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331004742/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|archive-date=2013-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>她表示自己想要制作那种陪伴她长大的音乐，也就是带有那种“90年代都市流行风”("urban pop, 90s music")的歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|title=Ariana Grande Talks Breakout Hit 'The Way': Watch New Music Video|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|publisher=Billboard|language=en|date=|accessdate=2013-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331004742/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|archive-date=2013-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑名本来定为“白日幻想”(Daydreamin)，计划于2013年8月发售。后来才改为现在的名称。<ref>{{cite web|author=Jason Lipshultz|title=Ariana Grande's 'Daydreamin'' Album Due In Late August|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/bbma-2013/1562988/ariana-grandes-daydreamin-album-due-in-late-august|publisher=[[普羅米修斯環球媒體|Prometheus Global Media]]|language=en|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2014-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221012904/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/bbma-2013/1562988/ariana-grandes-daydreamin-album-due-in-late-august|archive-date=2014-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>

