2013年6月，亞莉安娜终于完成了她的首张录音室专辑《挚爱》。<ref name=Daydreamin>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Finishes Recording First Album|url=http://www.fanlala.com/news/ariana-grande-finishes-recording-first-album|publisher=Fanlala|language=en|accessdate=2013-06-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702071145/http://www.fanlala.com/news/ariana-grande-finishes-recording-first-album|archivedate=2013-07-02}}</ref>专辑于9月1日在美国发售，9月2日在英国发售。<ref>{{cite web|author=Nickutopia Staff|title=Scooter Braun Makes An Announcement About Ariana Grande's "Yours Truly" Album|url=http://www.nickutopia.com/2013/07/23/scooter-braun-makes-an-announcement-about-ariana-grandes-yours-truly-album/|publisher=Nickutopia|language=en|date=|accessdate=2013-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727183639/http://www.nickutopia.com/2013/07/23/scooter-braun-makes-an-announcement-about-ariana-grandes-yours-truly-album/|archive-date=2013-07-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>《挚爱》在发售后的首周内卖出了138,000份，登上过[[告示板|告示板]]200强首位。<ref>{{cite news|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|title=Ariana Grande Debuts At No. 1 On Billboard 200|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687364/ariana-grande-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200|publisher=Billboard|language=en|date=|access-date=2013-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914022139/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5687364/ariana-grande-debuts-at-no-1-on-billboard-200|archive-date=2013-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.hitsdailydouble.com/sales/salescht.cgi |title=HITS Daily Double: Building Album Sales Chart<!-- Bot generated title --> |language=en |date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915012320/http://www.hitsdailydouble.com/sales/salescht.cgi |archivedate=2014-09-15 |access-date=2014-06-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2013/09/11/ariana-grande-tamar-braxton-score-top-debuts/|title=Ariana Grande, Tamar Braxton Score Top Debuts<!-- Bot generated title -->|publisher=Rap-Up.com|language=en|date=|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824175432/http://www.rap-up.com/2013/09/11/ariana-grande-tamar-braxton-score-top-debuts/|archive-date=2017-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>（有的中文转载报道写的数量是13万5千<ref>{{cite news |url=http://ent.cntv.cn/2013/09/12/ARTI1378948127886281.shtml |title=爱莉安娜·格兰德新专辑《Yours Truly》夺冠 |others=方嘉欣 (编辑), 李杰 (责任编辑) |publisher=环球网, [[央视网|央视网]] (转载网站) |language=zh-cn |date=2013-09-12 |access-date=2017-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231212139/http://ent.cntv.cn/2013/09/12/ARTI1378948127886281.shtml |archive-date=2017-12-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>）这使她成为了自[[凱莎|凱莎]]以来，第15位首张专辑直冲告示板榜首的女歌手。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5687385/ladies-first-quiz-ariana-grande-15-no-1-female-debut-albums |title=Ladies First Quiz: Ariana Grande & 15 No. 1 Female Debut Albums<!-- Bot generated title --> |publisher=Billboard |language=en |date= |access-date=2014-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106092349/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5687385/ladies-first-quiz-ariana-grande-15-no-1-female-debut-albums |archive-date=2017-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680143/ariana-grande-heading-for-top-of-billboard-200 |title=Ariana Grande Heading for Top of Billboard 200<!-- Bot generated title --> |publisher=Billboard |language=en |date= |access-date=2014-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110434/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5680143/ariana-grande-heading-for-top-of-billboard-200 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑的风格受到了许多艺人的影响，包括[[艾米·怀恩豪斯|艾米·怀恩豪斯]]、[[克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉|克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉]]、[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]和[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]等。<ref name="sheknows1" />亞莉安娜说这张专辑一半是对90年代[[节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]风的“回归”(throwback)，而另一半则是“完全由我自己原创的特色”。总的来说，她表示“所以有一半是回归，回归到那些非常熟悉的感觉，美好的感觉；另一半是我原创的，独具魅力，带有我喜爱的新鲜而美妙的感觉”。<ref>{{cite web |last=Vena |first=Jocelyn |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1711637/ariana-grande-yours-truly-album.jhtml |title=Ariana Grande Is Introducing The 'Real' Ariana On Yours Truly |publisher={{link-en|MTV News|MTV News}}. [[維亞康姆傳媒電視網|MTV Networks]] |language=en |date=2013-08-01 |accessdate=2013-08-02 |quote="...something that is very unique and very special that I've sort of written.","So half of it is a throwback and like very familiar feeling, feel-good, and then half of it is something that I've created that's sort of special and unique and refreshing and wonderful and I love it." |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804065147/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1711637/ariana-grande-yours-truly-album.jhtml |archive-date=2013-08-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年8月，她与[[詹妮特·麦柯迪|詹妮特·麦柯迪]]还一同主演了根据戈登·科曼(Gordon Korman)小说《骗局》(''Swindle'')改编的同名电影《骗局》。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.nick.com/celebrity/news/nick-stars-swindle-movie.html |title=News | New Deets on Swindle! |publisher=Nick.com |language=en |date= |accessdate=2013-02-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306123742/http://www.nick.com/celebrity/news/nick-stars-swindle-movie.html |archivedate=2013-03-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=AJ |last=Marechal |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118060202/ |title=Nick stars set to ‘Swindle’ |publisher=''[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]'' |language=en |date=2012-10-03 |accessdate=2013-02-27 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218232507/https://variety.com/2012/tv/news/nick-stars-set-to-swindle-1118060202/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月，她登上杂志《[[17_(美國雜誌)|Seventeen]]》的当月封面。<ref name="完美主义者">{{cite news |url=http://ent.china.com/music/wai/11057114/20130628/17917912.html |title=爱莉安娜·格兰德登《Seventeen》封面 |publisher=环球网 |language=zh-cn |date=2013-06-28 |accessdate=2017-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171231211941/http://ent.china.com/music/wai/11057114/20130628/17917912.html |archivedate=2017-12-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>格兰德在11月24日的[[2013年全美音乐奖|2013年全美音乐奖]]颁奖现场献艺并获得了“{{link-en|美国年度音乐新秀奖|American Music Award for New Artist of the Year}}”<ref name="ew.com">{{cite news |author= |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/11/25/amas-2013-winners-list/ |title=AMAs 2013: See the complete winners list |website=ew.com |language=en |date=2013-11-25 |accessdate=2013-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131126065635/http://music-mix.ew.com/2013/11/25/amas-2013-winners-list/ |archive-date=2013-11-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，且在当晚成为[[Twitter|Twitter]]最热话题人物，被提及的次数达到了231,966次。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gallo|first=Phil|title=Ariana Grande, Taylor Swift Lead AMAs to Record Twitter Traffic (Exclusive)|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5800827/amas-twitter-traffic-ariana-grande-taylor-swift|publisher=Billboard|language=en|date=|accessdate=2013-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213034358/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5800827/amas-twitter-traffic-ariana-grande-taylor-swift|archive-date=2013-12-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的热门单曲《方式》和《纹心》("Tattooed Heart")以及其宽广的[[音域|音域]]受到了人们赞赏。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1718029/ariana-grande-american-music-awards-performance-reviews.jhtml |title=Ariana Grande Smashed The American Music Awards, Just Ask Kelly Clarkson |language=en |date= |access-date=2014-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140313030529/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1718029/ariana-grande-american-music-awards-performance-reviews.jhtml |archive-date=2014-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

亞莉安娜曾在不少合唱团做过独唱艺人，也在纽约鸟岛(Birdland)俱乐部演唱过许多次。在[[佛罗里达美洲狮|佛罗里达美洲狮曲棍球队]]在[[福克斯电视台|福克斯电视台]]体育频道初登场时，亞莉安娜还为其献唱了[[美国国歌|美国国歌]]。亞莉安娜翻唱过[[玛丽亚·凯莉|玛丽亚·凯莉]]和[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]等明星的歌曲。

