.com/articles/news/5923162/aretha-franklin-ariana-grande-set-for-first-ladys-women-of-soul-concert|archive-date=2014-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/142984/R-E-S-P-E-C-T-Ariana-Grande-Star-Struck-After-Meeting-Aretha-Franklin-At-White-House|title=R-E-S-P-E-C-T! Ariana Grande Star-Struck After Meeting Aretha Franklin At White House|first=Alicia|last=Adejobi|publisher=Entertaimentwise|language=en|date=2014-03-07|accessdate=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308183439/http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/142984/R-E-S-P-E-C-T-Ariana-Grande-Star-Struck-After-Meeting-Aretha-Franklin-At-White-House|archive-date=2014-03-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年，亞莉安娜获得了{{link-en|音乐产业联合会|Music Business Association}}颁发的“年度突破性艺人奖”。这个奖表彰了亞莉安娜在2013年取得的成绩，包括其首专《挚爱》登上过[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|Billboard 200]]榜首，以及单曲《方式》挤入过前10强，并有2个[[白金唱片|白金唱片]]认证。不久后，亞莉安娜宣布她完成了第2张专辑的制作。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/144677/Very-Excited-For-These-Next-Few-Months-Ariana-Grande-Confirms-New-Album-Is-Done |title='Very Excited For These Next Few Months': Ariana Grande Confirms New Album Is Done! |publisher=entertainmentwise.com |language=en |date= |accessdate=2014-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413154543/http://www.entertainmentwise.com/news/144677/Very-Excited-For-These-Next-Few-Months-Ariana-Grande-Confirms-New-Album-Is-Done |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>第2张专辑的主打歌曲是与澳洲说唱艺人[[伊基·阿塞莉娅|伊基·阿塞莉娅]]合作<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726389/ariana-grande-teams-with-iggy-azalea-problems-see-cover-art.jhtml|last=Bobb|first=Maurice|title=Ariana Grande Teams With Iggy Azalea For 'Problems': See The Cover Art|newspaper=MTV News|language=en|date=2014-04-17|accessdate=2014-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420213943/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1726389/ariana-grande-teams-with-iggy-azalea-problems-see-cover-art.jhtml|archive-date=2014-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>的《{{link-en|难题 (爱莉安娜·格兰德演唱歌曲)|Problem (Ariana Grande song)|难题}}》("Problem")，于2014年4月27日在{{link-en|2014年电台迪斯尼音乐奖|2014 Radio Disney Music Awards}}上首演。<ref>{{cite web|last=Pambid|first=Diadem|title=Ariana Grande's New Single 'Problem' Allegedly About Ex-boyfriend, Jai Brooks?|url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/548485/20140417/ariana-grande-problem-jai-brooks-jariana.htm#.U09Dcl6Wt8N|publisher=International Business Times AU|language=en|date=|accessdate=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140417230315/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/548485/20140417/ariana-grande-problem-jai-brooks-jariana.htm#.U09Dcl6Wt8N|archive-date=2014-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>《难题》在发售后的第1周获得了438,000次的下载量，使她成为新曲发布后1周内下载量超过40万的最年轻女艺人。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6077517/ariana-grande-problem-record-sales-debut-hot-100-chart |title=Problem, sales debut |publisher=Billboard |language=en |date= |access-date=2014-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623010312/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6077517/ariana-grande-problem-record-sales-debut-hot-100-chart |archive-date=2018-06-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这首歌在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|Billboard Hot 100]]上位列第2），是她的第2首打入[[告示板|告示板]]前10位的歌曲，也被赞为史上最热首发女艺人合作歌曲，至今在Youtube上已突破1,000,000,000 點閱率。<ref>{{cite news |author=Gary Trust |title=John Legend's 'All Of Me' Tops Hot 100, Ariana Grande Debuts At No. 3 |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6077635/hot-100-john-legend-all-of-me-ariana-grande-iggy-azalea |website=[[告示板|告示板]]官方网站 |language=en |date=2014-05-07 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140510180721/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6077635/hot-100-john-legend-all-of-me-ariana-grande-iggy-azalea |archive-date=2014-05-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2014年6月28日，亞莉安娜宣布其第2张专辑将于2014年8月25日发售，取名为《我的所有》(''My Everything'')。主打歌<<我的所有>>是獻给当时已故但非常疼爱亞莉安娜的爺爺，每当亞莉安娜演唱时都因掛念爺爺而不禁落泪。亞莉安娜也提到了她与大肖恩合作的另一首歌曲《最佳错误》("Best Mistake")。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Announces Exclusive Concert!|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NorphRjDAyc|website=Youtube|language=en|date=|access-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824184806/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NorphRjDAyc|archive-date=2014-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Grande|first1=Ariana|title=#7DaysUntilBreakFree #60DaysUntilMyNewAlbum|url=https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/481934658213404672|website=Twitter|language=en|date=2014-06-25|access-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714180353/https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/481934658213404672|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

