=== 2018年-至今：《甜到翻 (Sweetener)》及《謝謝，下一位 (Thank U, Next)》 ===
2016年，亞莉安娜开始与[[法瑞尔·威廉姆斯|法瑞尔·威廉姆斯]]一同开始展开专辑的制作工作，但“曼彻斯特事件严重影响了该项目的预期”<ref name="Fader2018" />。2018年4月20日，爱莉安娜發行了即将发行的第四张錄音室專輯的首支單曲《[[淚已流乾|淚已流乾]]》，並同時發佈了歌曲的音乐影片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/hear-ariana-grandes-uplifting-new-song-no-tears-left-to-cry-w519323|title=Hear Ariana Grande's Uplifting New Song 'No Tears Left to Cry'|date=2018-04-20|last=Reed|first=Ryan|work=Rolling Stone|access-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521094303/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/hear-ariana-grandes-uplifting-new-song-no-tears-left-to-cry-w519323|archive-date=2018-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，歌曲空降《告示牌》百強單曲榜第三位，成為了亞莉安娜第九首進入該榜單前十的歌曲，也使得亞莉安娜成为了唯一一位每张专辑的首支单曲都进入该榜单前十的艺人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8412480/drake-nice-for-what-hot-100-number-one-ariana-grande-j-cole|title=Drake Leads ''Billboard'' Hot 100, Ariana Grande Arrives at No. 3 & J. Cole Collects Record Three Debuts in Top 10|date=2018-04-30|last=Trust|first=Gary|work=Billboard|access-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329054545/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8412480/drake-nice-for-what-hot-100-number-one-ariana-grande-j-cole|archive-date=2019-03-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月1日，她在《今夜秀》上表演了歌曲《淚已流乾》，并宣佈了专辑名为《[[甜到翻|甜到翻]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/watch-ariana-grande-cover-kendrick-in-the-style-of-evanescence-on-fallon|title=Watch Ariana Grande Cover Kendrick in the Style of Evanescence on ''Fallon''|date=2018-05-01|first=Braudie|work=Pitchfork|last1=Blais-Billie|last2=Minsker|first2=Evan|access-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503235908/https://pitchfork.com/news/watch-ariana-grande-cover-kendrick-in-the-style-of-evanescence-on-fallon/|archive-date=2018-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年6月20日，专辑开启了预购，并发行了饒舌歌手[[妮琪·米娜|妮琪·米娜]]伴唱的歌曲《[[曙光来临|曙光来临]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://people.com/music/ariana-grande-the-light-is-coming-music-video-nicki-minaj|title=Ariana Grande Drops 'The Light Is Coming' Video, Frolics in the Woods with Nicki Minaj|date=2018-06-20|last=Nelson|first=Jeff|work=People|access-date=2018-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710173623/https://people.com/music/ariana-grande-the-light-is-coming-music-video-nicki-minaj/|archive-date=2018-07-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月13日，专辑的第二支单曲《[[上帝是女人|上帝是女人]]》发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2018/07/listen-to-ariana-grandes-new-song-god-is-a-woman.html|title=Listen to Ariana Grande's New Song 'God is a woman'|accessdate=2018-07-13|last=Kiefer|first=Halle|work=Vulture|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713072630/http://www.vulture.com/2018/07/listen-to-ariana-grandes-new-song-god-is-a-woman.html|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8465375/ariana-grande-epic-god-is-a-woman-video-decoded|title=Ariana Grande's Epic 'God Is a Woman' Video, Decoded|date=2018-07-13|last=Whittum|first=Connor|work=Billboard|access-date=2018-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826065308/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8465375/ariana-grande-epic-god-is-a-woman-video-decoded|archive-date=2018-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>，该单曲在《公告牌》百强单曲榜上最高达到第八名，成为了亞莉安娜第十支进入该榜单前十的歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8472538/ariana-grande-10th-top-10-hit-10-songs-billboard-hot-100-chart|title=Ariana Grande Earns 10th Top 10 Hit, Lands 10 Songs on ''Billboard'' Hot 100|accessdate=2018-08-27|date=2018-08-27|last=Zellner|first=Xander|work=Billboard|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828011733/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8472538/ariana-grande-10th-top-10-hit-10-songs-billboard-hot-100-chart|archive-date=2018-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年7月13日，专辑发行，亞莉安娜随即在纽约、芝加哥、洛杉矶和伦敦开始了四场名为“{{Le|The Sweetener Sessions|The Sweetener Sessions}}”的专辑宣传演唱会<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ariana-gran