.com/uk/entertainment/a24255798/ariana-grande-bbc-special/|archive-date=2018-10-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AtTheBBC">{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/stayingin/tvfilm/ariana-grande-at-the-bbc-why-davina-mccall-s-chat-with-star-is-a-must-watch-a3978191.html|title=Ariana Grande at the BBC: Why Davina McCall’s chat with star is a must watch|date=2018-11-01|last=Sporn|first=Natasha|website=Evening Standard|access-date=2018-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181104131340/https://www.standard.co.uk/stayingin/tvfilm/ariana-grande-at-the-bbc-why-davina-mccall-s-chat-with-star-is-a-must-watch-a3978191.html|archive-date=2018-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，亞莉安娜还宣布《{{Le|甜到翻世界巡回演唱会|Sweetener World Tour}}》将于2019年3月18日始于纽约州奥尔巴尼，北美的巡演将持续到6月。

