== 艺术风格 ==
=== 音乐风格 ===
[[File:Mariah_Carey_Neighborhood_Ball_in_downtown_Washington_2009_cropped.JPG|thumb]]对亞莉安娜影响很大。]]
{{Quote box|width=25em||align=right|style=padding:8px|quote=“我喜爱玛丽亚·凯莉。甚至可以说她是这个星球上我最喜欢的人了。当然啦，[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]也是我大爱。只要高音艺术不衰败，惠妮和玛丽亚的影响力就会持续地渗透下去。我也喜欢菲姬。她人很有趣，也满怀着激情。我也很喜欢她能rap得如此的好。就仿佛，她那嗓音仿佛是一个奇迹，不需要太多的努力，便可做到在G调和A调间收放自如地歌唱。她只要随口一唱，我就感觉很惊艳了。”<br>("I love Mariah Carey. She is literally my favorite human being on the planet. And of course Whitney Houston as well. As far as vocal influences go, Whitney and Mariah pretty much cover it. I love Fergie as well. She's just so fun and passionate. I love that she raps as well. Like, she has a fantastic voice and she can belt Gs and As and she doesn’t have to do it all the time. She just has swag and I think that's really cool.")|source= 亞莉安娜在论及自己的音乐为哪些人物所影响过时曾这样谈到。<ref name=Influences1/>
}}

亞莉安娜的歌曲主要属于[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行]]和[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]，且带有一些[[放克|放克]]、[[舞曲|舞曲]]和[[嘻哈音樂|嘻哈]]等类型的元素。<ref name=TheBillboard>{{cite news|first=Jason|last=Lipshutz|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|title=Ariana Grande Talks Breakout Hit 'The Way': Watch New Music Video|language=en|date=2013-03-28|accessdate=2013-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331004742/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/1554921/ariana-grande-talks-breakout-hit-the-way-watch-new-music-video|archive-date=2013-03-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=allmusic>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/ariana-grande-mn0002264745|title=Ariana Grande – Overview|publisher=[[Allmusic|AllMusic]]|language=en|date=|accessdate=2013-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130427020057/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/ariana-grande-mn0002264745|archive-date=2013-04-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>她是听着[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]和{{link-en|90年代音乐|90s music}}长大的。<ref name=TheBillboard/><ref name=Influences2/>其音乐起初定位的听众对象是青少年群体，这一点能够从朝气蓬勃的{{link-en|泡泡糖流行乐|bubblegum pop}}风格单曲《捧起你的心》中得以体现。<ref name="AllMisicBio">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/ariana-grande-mn0002264745/biography|title=Artist Biography by Stephen Thomas Erlewine|publisher=[[Allmusic|AllMusic]]|language=en|date=|accessdate=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726185301/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/ariana-grande-mn0002264745/biography|archive-date=2014-07-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>首张专辑《挚爱》借鉴了许多90年代的音乐元素，<ref>{{cite web |last=Vena |first=Jocelyn |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1711637/ariana-grande-yours-truly-album.jhtml |title=Ariana Grande Is Introducing The 'Real' Ariana On Yours Truly |publisher=MTV News, MTV Networks |language=en |date=2013-08-01 |accessdate=2013-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804065147/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1711637/ariana-grande-yours-truly-album.jhtml |archive-date=2013-08-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在制作过程中也得到了90年代R&B音乐制作人[[娃娃脸_(艺人)|娃娃脸]]的帮助。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/my-everything-mw0002698499|title=My Everything – Ariana Grande|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|publisher=AllMusic|language=en|date=2014-08-25|accessdate=2014-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829165315/http://www.allmusic.com/album/my-everything-mw0002698499|archive-date=2014-08-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后于2014年发售的专辑《我的所有》开始向[[电子舞曲|電子舞曲]] 和[[電子流行|電子流行]]的方向探索，被视为其风格的一次突破。<ref name="RSMyETReview">{{cite web|author=Rob Sheffield|title=Ariana Grande My Everything|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/ariana-grande-my-everything-20140826|work=''Rolling Stone''|language=en|date=2014-08-26|accessdate=2014-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140828033451/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/ariana-grande-my-everything-20140826|archive-date=2014-08-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

亞莉安娜提到自己小时候受到过古巴裔美国艺人[[格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡|格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡]]的影响。在亞莉安娜8岁那年，格洛丽亚·埃斯特凡在一艘游船上观看了她的节目表演后对她大加赞赏，亞莉安娜从那时开始便萌生了以后想进入音乐圈发展的梦想。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nick-kids.net/post/74685927172/when-i-was-eight-years-old-i-was-on-a-cruise-ship |title=Nickelodeon Kids |publisher=Nickelodeon Kids |language=en |date=2013-01-26 |accessdate=2013-01-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001071524/http://nick-kids.net/post/74685927172/when-i-was-eight-years-old-i-was-on-a-cruise-ship |archivedate=2014-10-01 }}</ref>她说[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]对她影响也很大，她是从小便在休斯顿的音乐的熏陶下长大的。休斯顿的音乐是她的无尽的灵感来源。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2014/03/07/ariana-grande-covers-whitney-houston-at-the-white-house/#more-181197 |title=Ariana Grande Covers Whitney Houston at the White House |publisher=Rap-Up.com |language=en |date= |accessdate=2014-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816105553/http://www.rap-up.com/2014/03/07/ariana-grande-covers-whitney-houston-at-the-white-house/#more-181197 |archive-date=2014-08-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>亞莉安娜也说休斯顿是她走上歌唱之路的原因。她还说[[布兰蒂|布兰蒂]]对她的影响也不小，特别是后者音乐中的"riffs"元素。<ref name="billboard.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5748215/gimme-five-ariana-grandes-most-inspirational-female-singers |title=Gimme Five: Ariana Grande's Most Inspirational Female Singers |publisher=Billboard |language=en |date=2013-10-09 |accessdate=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714114319/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5748215/gimme-five-ariana-grandes-most-inspirational-female-singers |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其他被她提及的影响过她的歌手还有[[麦当娜|麦当娜]]、[[天命真女|天命真女]]、[[菲姬|菲姬·杜默]]、[[克莉丝汀·阿奎莱拉|克莉丝汀·阿奎莱拉]]、[[印蒂雅·艾瑞|印蒂雅·艾瑞]]、[[伊莫珍·希普|伊莫珍·希普]]及[[艾米·怀恩豪斯|艾米·怀恩豪斯]]。<ref name=Influences1/><ref name=Influences2/><ref name=Vmagazine>{{cite web |url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/02/21/ariana-grande-v-magazine-pics/ |title=Ariana Grande Strips Down To Lingerie For Sexy ‘V’ Shoot |publisher=Hollywoodlife |language=en |date=2014-02-21 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221204718/http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/02/21/ariana-grande-v-magazine-pics/ |archive-date=2014-02-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.disneydreaming.com/2013/07/21/ariana-grande-names-her-debut-album-yours-truly/ |title=Ariana Grande Names Her Debut Album "Yours Truly" |publisher=Disney Dreaming |language=en |date=2013-07-21 |accessdate=2013-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230235626/http://www.disneydreaming.com/2013/07/21/ariana-grande-names-her-debut-album-yours-truly/ |archive-date=2013-12-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>亞莉安娜也说过[[大肖恩|大肖恩]]是自己最喜欢的[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]歌手。<ref name=TheBillboard/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vmagazine.com/site/content/2304/grande-dame|title=Interview Vmagazine-Ariana Grande|work=''V magazine''|language=en|date=|accessdate=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6R1UbAhnL?url=http://www.vmagazine.com/site/content/2304/grande-dame|archive-date=2014-07-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

