 to Stop Comparing Ariana Grande to Mariah Carey|last=Horowitz|first=Steven J.|work=Billboard|language=en|date=2014-08-27|accessdate=2014-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140830003318/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6229461/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-comparisons|archive-date=2014-08-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[告示板|告示板]]》杂志评论员Julianne Escobedo Shepherd在类比二者的同时，还补充说凯莉和亞莉安娜“都拥有一种其声音就像是会说话一般的才能”。<ref name="BBFashion">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6229387/ariana-grande-fashion-style-my-everything|title=Ariana Grande's Fashion Focus: Breaking Down Her Many Confident Looks|last=Shepherd|first=Julianne Escobedo|work=Billboard|language=en|date=2014-08-26|accessdate=2014-09-02|quote="...got the talent to let their vocals do the talking...","That's not where the similarities end. [...] Grande is subverting it with cute, comfortable, and on-trend dresses with a feminine slant."|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831033945/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6229387/ariana-grande-fashion-style-my-everything|archive-date=2014-08-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>Shepherd还说“相似点还不止这些...（但）格兰德的形象倒是独树一帜。她总以一副可爱、自在且时尚的装束亮相，还有些小女人味。”<ref name="BBFashion"/>亞莉安娜本人则觉得别人拿自己和玛丽亚·凯莉作比较是对自己的“高度称赞”("huge compliment")和“祝福”("blessing")，<ref name=Vmagazine /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a516168/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-comparison-is-a-blessing.html|title=Ariana Grande: 'Mariah Carey comparison is a blessing'|first=Justin|last=Harp|language=en|date=2013-09-17|accessdate=2013-11-30|quote="I mean, it's a huge compliment, but when you hear my entire album, you'll see that Mariah's sound is much different than mine."|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203030841/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a516168/ariana-grande-mariah-carey-comparison-is-a-blessing.html|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>还常说自己的作品风格主要是受到了玛丽亚·凯莉和惠特妮·休斯顿的影响。<ref name=AboutAriana/><ref name=Influences