d: So, I guess it's obvious ... |last=Skyes |first=Nathan |publisher= |language=en |date=2013-09-25 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022160302/https://twitter.com/NathanTheWanted/status/382531060103278592 |archive-date=2013-10-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/382531432536489985 |title=Twitter / ArianaGrande: we hesitated saying anything ... |author=Ariana Grande |publisher= |language=en |date=2013-09-25 |accessdate=2013-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001081248/https://twitter.com/ArianaGrande/status/382531432536489985 |archive-date=2013-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=|title=Ariana Grande Hopes Justin Bieber Can "Grow Into His Manhood Without Getting Hurt"|url=http://b96.cbslocal.com/2014/01/23/ariana-grande-hopes-justin-bieber-can-grow-into-his-manhood-without-getting-hurt/#.UuHmxZFyHBY.twitter|publisher=B96.com|language=en|date=|accessdate=2014-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126121830/http://b96.cbslocal.com/2014/01/23/ariana-grande-hopes-justin-bieber-can-grow-into-his-manhood-without-getting-hurt/#.UuHmxZFyHBY.twitter|archive-date=2014-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年初，曾有传闻说格兰德与Jai Brooks恢复了恋爱关系。5月2日，这个消息得到了证实，一些八卦网站发布了他们接吻的照片。<ref>{{cite web|last=Marquina|first=Sierra|title=Ariana Grande Is Back With Ex Jai Brooks, Confirms Duet With Justin Bieber|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ariana-grande-back-with-ex-boyfriend-confirms-duet-with-justin-bieber-201425|publisher=''Us Weekly''|language=en|date=|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503012345/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ariana-grande-back-with-ex-boyfriend-confirms-duet-with-justin-bieber-201425|archive-date=2014-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>但3个月后，又传出他们再次分手的消息。<ref>{{cite web|last=Marquina|first=Sierra|title=Ariana Grande and Boyfriend Jai Brooks Split Again: Breakup Details|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ariana-grande-and-boyfriend-jai-brooks-split-breakup-details-201448|publisher=''Us Weekly''|language=en|date=2014-08-05|accessdate=2014-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805182510/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/ariana-grande-and-boyfriend-jai-brooks-split-breakup-details-201448|archive-date=2014-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年10月13日，也即在经过多家媒体两个多月的跟踪报道后，格兰德首次确认她已與[[当代节奏布鲁斯|節奏藍調]]歌手[[大肖恩|大肖恩]]相恋。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Strecker|title=Ariana Grande Confirms Relationship With Big Sean|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6281641/ariana-grande-confirms-big-sean-dating|language=en|date=2014-10-13|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115083557/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6281641/ariana-grande-confirms-big-sean-dating|archive-date=2015-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Vulpo|first1=Mike|title=Ariana Grande Finally Confirms She's Dating Big Sean, Calls Him an "Amazing" Man|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/588034/ariana-grande-finally-confirms-she-s-dating-big-sean-calls-him-an-amazing-man|website=E! Online|language=en|date=2014-10-13|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106043251/http://www.eonline.com/news/588034/ariana-grande-finally-confirms-she-s-dating-big-sean-calls-him-an-amazing-man|archive-date=2015-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>相处八个月后，两人分手。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://celebrity.yahoo.com/news/ariana-grande-big-sean-split-8-months-dating-160000984-us-weekly.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150427143334/https://celebrity.yahoo.com/news/ariana-grande-big-sean-split-8-months-dating-160000984-us-weekly.html|archivedate=2015-04-27|title=Ariana Grande, Big Sean Split After 8 Months of Dating: Breakup Details|work=Yahoo Celebrity|language=en|date=2015-04-20|accessdate=2015-04-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2016年末，格兰德开始与之前合作过的歌手[[麥克·米勒|麥克·米勒]]交往。但在2018年與他分手。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.vogue.com/13484221/mac-miller-the-divine-feminine-album |title=Mac Miller on Love, Ariana Grande, and the Last Thing That Made Him Cry |author=Patricia Garcia |publisher=''[[时尚_(杂志)|Vogue]]'' |language=en |date=2016-09-27 |access-date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103170159/http://www.vogue.com/13484221/mac-miller-the-divine-feminine-album/ |archive-date=2017-01-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2016/09/ariana-grande-wraps-her-legs-around-mac-miller-in-photo.html |author=Theresa Avila |title=Ariana Grande Confirms Her Relationship With Mac Miller by Literally Wrapping Her Legs Around Him |publisher=''{{link-en|New York (magazine)|纽约 (杂志)|New York}}'' |language=en |date=2016-09-07 |access-date= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329014729/http://nymag.com/thecut/2016/09/ariana-grande-wraps-her-legs-around-mac-miller-in-photo.html |archive-date=2017-03-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2018年5月，她開始與週六夜現場的喜劇演員[[皮特·戴維森|皮特·戴維森]]交往，並一度訂婚，但因前男友麥克·米勒死訊傳出後，於2018年11月，兩人宣布分手。2020年5月，爱莉安娜在[[YouTube|YouTube]]发布她和[[贾斯丁·比伯|贾斯丁·比伯]]所合唱的《[[如胶似漆|如胶似漆]]》里发现她和新的男友交往。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.onefm.com.my/ariana-grande%E8%AE%A4%E7%88%B1%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8Cmv%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B8%E6%8B%A5%E6%99%92%E6%81%A9%E7%88%B1/ |title=ARIANA GRANDE认爱了！新歌MV与男友相拥晒恩爱 |work=[[One_FM|One FM]] |language=zh |date=2020-05-09 |accessdate=2020-05-09 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305171602/https://www.onefm.com.my/ariana-grande%E8%AE%A4%E7%88%B1%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%81%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8Cmv%E4%B8%8E%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E7%9B%B8%E6%8B%A5%E6%99%92%E6%81%A9%E7%88%B1/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>新的男友为房地产商，Dalton Gomez。2020年12月21日，她在[[Instagram|Instagram]]宣布订婚。2021年5月15日，兩人舉辦了一個小型的私人婚禮，並於5月26日在Instagram上發布婚禮現場的照片<ref>{{Cite web|title=Inside Ariana Grande’s Intimate At-Home Wedding|url=https://www.vogue.com/slideshow/ariana-grande-at-home-wedding-photos|access-date=2021-05-26|last=Macon|first=Alexandra|work=Vogue|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://