== 荣誉 ==
{{Main|:en:List of awards and nominations received by Ariana Grande|l1=亞莉安娜·格蘭德獲獎及提名獎項列表}}

亞莉安娜获得过12次[[葛萊美獎|格莱美奖]]的候选提名並獲得2座，<ref>{{cite web|title=Grammys 2015: And the Nominees Are…|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/6363565/grammys-2015-nominations-57th-annual|website=Billboard|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520064021/http://www.billboard.com/articles/6363565/grammys-2015-nominations-57th-annual|archive-date=2015-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>她得过的几个主要音乐奖项包括3个[[美国音乐奖|全美音樂獎]]（{{lang-en|American Music Award}}）,<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande's 2013 American Music Awards Performance Earns Praise From Lady Gaga and Ciara|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/484560/ariana-grande-s-2013-american-music-awards-performance-earns-praise-from-lady-gaga-and-ciara|website=E! Online|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101220130/http://www.eonline.com/news/484560/ariana-grande-s-2013-american-music-awards-performance-earns-praise-from-lady-gaga-and-ciara|archive-date=2015-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>9个[[MTV视频音乐奖|MTV视频音乐奖]]（{{lang-en|MTV Video Music Award}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=2014 MTV Video Music Awards — Winners List|url=http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2014/08/2014-mtv-video-music-awards-winners-list/|website=ABC News|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112160032/http://abcnews.go.com/blogs/entertainment/2014/08/2014-mtv-video-music-awards-winners-list/|archive-date=2015-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>和2个[[MTV欧洲音乐奖|MTV欧洲音乐奖]]（{{lang-en|MTV Europe Music Awards}}）。2014年，她获得了2014年度[[告示板|告示板]]新兴音乐女星奖（{{lang-en|''Billboard'''s Women in Music Award as a Rising Star}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=Women in Music's Rising Star Ariana Grande Shares Her Mother's Most Important Lesson|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/women-in-music-2014/6405617/ariana-grande-rising-star-women-in-music|website=Billboard|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150103001005/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/women-in-music-2014/6405617/ariana-grande-rising-star-women-in-music|archive-date=2015-01-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2015年格兰德获得了[[全美音樂獎|全美音樂獎]]（{{lang-en|American Music Awards}}）的最喜爱的女歌手奖<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theamas.com/winners/2015-winners/|title=2015 Winners - American Music Awards|author=|publisher="dick clark productions"|language=en|year=2015|accessdate=2015-01-11|quote=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124002058/http://www.theamas.com/winners/2015-winners/|archive-date=2015-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，她獲得[[第61屆格萊美獎|格莱美奖]]的兩項提名，分別為「最佳流行演唱專輯」（[[甜到翻|甜到翻]]）及「最佳流行歌手」（[[上帝是女人|上帝是女人]]），最終拿下「最佳流行演唱專輯」的獎項，這也是她首次獲得[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande Reacts to Winning First GRAMMY Despite Slamming Academy|url=https://www.etonline.com/ariana-grande-reacts-to-winning-first-grammy-despite-slamming-academy-119301|website=ET|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211053527/https://www.etonline.com/ariana-grande-reacts-to-winning-first-grammy-despite-slamming-academy-119301|archive-date=2019-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年，她入圍9項[[公告牌音乐奖|告示牌音樂獎]]，並獲得「最佳女藝人」及「[[告示牌音樂獎排行榜成就獎|告示牌音樂獎排行榜成就獎]]」，是首次獲得告示牌音樂獎。

影视方面，她因所主演的《萨姆与卡特》一剧获得过尼克卡特频道儿童选择奖（{{lang-en|Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Award}}）之最佳女演员奖（{{lang-en|Best Actress}}）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Double win! Ariana Grande nabs Favourite TV Actress honor at Kids' Choice Awards as she hits a fashion high note in chic yellow frock|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2592584/Ariana-Grande-nabs-Favourite-TV-Actress-honor-Kids-Choice-Awards-woos-audiences-chic-cheery-yellow-ensemble.html|website=Daily Mail UK|language=en|date=|access-date=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150101220316/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2592584/Ariana-Grande-nabs-Favourite-TV-Actress-honor-Kids-Choice-Awards-woos-audiences-chic-cheery-yellow-ensemble.html|archive-date=2015-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

